summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 69E, page 166 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in portions of Lots 17, 18 and 19, Block 7, Steel Plant Add. lying south of W. Orchard St., located on the southwest and southeast corners of Delridge Way and W. Orchard St., from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Community Business (BC) Zone.
